Package edu.ncsu.csc216.issue_manager.model.manager

Class IssueList

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.issue_manager.model.manager.IssueList
  • public class IssueList
extends java.lang.Object
    Concrete class that maintains a current list of Issues in the Issue Manager system. These issues are ordered by id and duplicate ids are not allowed. A IssueList maintains a List of Issues. IssueList also maintains a counter which represents the id of the next Issue added to the list.
    Author:
    symone
